
pciutils: PCI bus installed cards detection of Video, Network, Disk cards

Installation
$ sudo yum install -y pciutils

Management
$ sudo systemctl status pcid

Usage
$ lspci 
$ lspci -nn
$ lspci -mm
$ lspci -v
NOTE: detailed info
$ lspci -t
NOTE: bus diagram as a tree
$ lspci -d <vendor:device>
$ lspci -s <domain:bus:slot.func>
NOTE: device by detail
$ lspci -k
NOTE: kernel modules


